            <title>[SPR-6474] JavaConfig - provide more tooling when working with a FactoryBean implementation</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-6474</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Please consider that you need to declare an EntityManagerFactory using JavaConfig.&lt;/p&gt;

